Ad Text:
The Role
 
This is a key leadership role that leads the data and analytics stream of our clients SAP S/4HANA ERP transformation. It is responsible for building a strong data foundation, delivering reliable reporting, and shaping an AI/GenAI strategy to support future growth. The role drives cross-functional initiatives to enable data-driven decisions, ensure high-quality data migration, and implement advanced analytics aligned with business needs.
 
Key Responsibilities

Develop and lead the data and analytics strategy to support a large-scale ERP transformation;
Establish data governance frameworks, ownership models, and standards to ensure accuracy, compliance, and accountability;
Oversee selection and implementation of tools and platforms for master data management, reporting, and analytics;
Define and maintain data architecture to support ERP, reporting, and AI capabilities;
Lead the planning and execution of data migration, ensuring quality and integrity across phased deployments;
Drive the design and delivery of enterprise reporting and insights, enabling data-driven decision-making across the business;
Shape the roadmap for incorporating AI and GenAI into business processes responsibly and effectively; and
Manage delivery of all data & analytics workstreams, coordinating with internal teams and partners to achieve program milestones.
About You

Extensive experience in data analytics, enterprise reporting, and large-scale SAP ERP transformations;
Strong expertise in data migration, governance, and reporting within ERP environments;
Knowledge of master data management and governance practices, with exposure to relevant tools;
Familiarity with emerging technologies such as AI/ML and their application in business;
Proven leadership skills with the ability to influence, engage stakeholders, and drive change;
Strategic yet pragmatic, with a track record of delivering outcomes in complex, fast-paced programs; and
Collaborative and resilient, with excellent communication skills and a focus on data quality and integrity.
